Building applications:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look at the example files to see how this is done.

* Create an ApplicationXXX class that extends 'Application' class
* Create XML build-file
* Run './bin/application-gen'
* Copy './src/build/apps/app.XXX.js' to './public_html/js/'
* Copy './src/build/apps/app.XXX.css' to './public_html/css/'
